data.description:
Charming 3 bedroom 2 bath home awaits it's New Family! In the Highly desired Mansfield school District. Laminate wood flooring throughout with tons of Natural sunlight open floorplan with split bedrooms. Close to shopping and Restaurants.
HVAC system updated to 3-Ton in 2022, solar screens for energy efficiency, solar panels also in 2022, Roof replaced in 2022, dishwasher replaced 2022
Refrigerator is Negotiable
 Don't Miss out on this move in ready home.
